{"tid":225100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有冇人鐘意釣魚？？？","createTime":"2017-05-01T13:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T18:50:05.000Z","uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd8653085103f38a874881c60c77caf4501bfc7","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"放假有乜做？<br />\n毒係屋企打機？日日stalk你女神IG Facebook?<br />\n反正假期無野做<br />\n不如出黎同一班巴打做浪子釣下魚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好以為釣魚只係中佬既活動<br />\n其實釣魚係香港已經越黎越流行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你怕掂到生勾勾 戇鳩鳩既魚餌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以玩Lure <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你鐘意出海吹下海風？<br />\n你可以跟巴打們一齊出海釣魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你只係一個新手甚至從未釣過魚？<br />\n我地群入邊有玩開唔同釣法既巴打<br />\n唔識教到你識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩話？你怕醜？<br />\n群內有既巴打由16歲到40歲都有<br />\n你仲怕咩？<br />\n群入邊每個巴打都好熱心，唔會小圈子無人會被忽略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n群組由上年年中開立<br />\n到家陣大大小小都搞過好多次釣魚活動<br />\n由碼頭釣魚到上魚排釣魚再到出外海都有！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗諗咁多啦！心動不如行動啦！<br />\n禁下邊條link就立即傳送到釣魚佬既集中地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEFi7AjUDnYv1lQq_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEFi7AjUDnYv1lQq_A&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e6d6fb4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEFi7AjUDnYv1lQq_A</a>"},{"pid":"3d3ca3749b70996abdf683287ac201fe627bf6bf","tid":225100,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"無知一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佛枝魚竿會唔會勾到頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3568c43dd73ecfcf418dfb536dc4f18117c2612","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佛枝魚竿會唔會勾到頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定唔會，放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以跟我地試下釣魚"},{"pid":"c567b868718f586d3dc82f95f916daf52a41dc88","tid":225100,"uid":60687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"自從讀完中學就冇釣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c3e748af0ec70ec24b16adca8cd6a342ba95f1","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從讀完中學就冇釣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n釣魚幾多歲都可以釣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69781e8f07f12b6354e17468d31b07a9aab6b74a","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb493ecc5bc933e180a8246ef9585ac682e7cf96","tid":225100,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"讀書上堂就話釣魚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdb65544000f055ea7b67b88ea34a0abb01019c","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"412971c98fede26ff328a3ccbef9c10ff61cff16","tid":225100,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9304a357198e321e0ba58637c39ba05ae36d6124","tid":225100,"uid":15